App-Normalo version 0.03
========================

App::Normalo normalizes filenames to kebab-case format. It converts
spaces, underscores, and other separators to hyphens, lowercases all
characters, transliterates UTF-8 to ASCII, and removes special characters.

The module can be used as a library (App::Normalo::convert) or via the
normalo command-line tool to rename files in batch.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Text::Unidecode

